Package edu.ncsu.csc216.pack_scheduler.user

Class Student

java.lang.Object
edu.ncsu.csc216.pack_scheduler.user.User
edu.ncsu.csc216.pack_scheduler.user.Student
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Student>
public class Student extends User implements Comparable<Student>
Represents a Student, getting its max credits, schedule, and whether a Student can add a Course Extends the User super class and implements the Comparable interface to compare two Students
Author:
Peyton Herring, Arnav Ganguly, Aaron Green
